        <h2>
            国家与社会革命的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 20 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1495030">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1495030/" class="title-link">用革命结束革命</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1495030"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1679535-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">维舟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-09-12"
      class="main-meta">2008-09-12 09:42:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1495030_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  近五百年来的各国历史，基本上就是它们如何实现现代化的历史。这其中有一个不容忽视的现象，即荷兰、英国、美国、日本等海洋型国家的转变完成得比较顺利，而三个大陆型国家法、俄、中，则都是在经过长期痛苦、代价高昂的流血革命之后，才最终脱胎换骨，完成对国家和社会的重新...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1495030/#comments">(19回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">62有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1495030_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1495030_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6323405">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6323405/" class="title-link">当谈论比较历史时我们在谈论什么</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6323405"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiujiangmingbo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2325751-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiujiangmingbo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">秋江暝泊</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-11"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-11 20:15:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6323405_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  研究生院的方法课是一种蛮奇怪的存在。就像其他的graduate seminar一样，课上基本上不告诉你任何定论，而是把你当作成熟的研究者，直接把你带入到学术圈重要的辩论中去。但对于一个急切的想知道做研究是什么样子的、怎么上手做研究的一年级学生来说，直接读那种在方法论上吵来...

